definition: classifier for gifts, newspaper, magazine, papers, reports, contracts etc/variant of 分[fen4]

sentences.english: For the study, published in the September issue of Pediatrics, researchers identified 28 babies who spent time in the NICU and were later diagnosed with an autism spectrum disorder.
sentences.chinese: 这项研究发表在九月份的《儿科》杂志上面。

sentences.english: The suspected criminal is being hunted by police following a burglary in Swansea in September.
sentences.chinese: 这名疑犯因涉嫌九月份在斯旺西行窃被警方通缉。

sentences.english: RESULTS The contents of chlorogenic acid was the highest in June and the lowest in September.
sentences.chinese: 结果绿原酸的含量在六月份最高，九月份最低。

sentences.english: There was only one way to make the AL East interesting in September.
sentences.chinese: 只有一条路可以使美联东区在九月份是精采的。

sentences.english: He will start his new civilian job at the CIA in September.
sentences.chinese: 他将在九月份开始他在中央情报局的新的文职工作。

sentences.english: Both polls were postponed because of Hurricane Gustav, which pounded Louisiana in September.
sentences.chinese: 两次选举均因为飓风九月份袭击路易斯安那州而推迟。

sentences.english: When the Senate passed the bill in September, it achieved a veto-proof majority.
sentences.chinese: 当下议院在九月份通过提案时，就满足了反对的条件。

sentences.english: GDI has been repeatedly patched by Microsoft, most recently in September.
sentences.chinese: 微软已经多次修补GDI，最新的一次在九月份。

sentences.english: The Japanese even have a National Chrysanthemum Day on September 9, known as the Festival of Happiness.
sentences.chinese: 在九月份日本人有一个全国菊花日，也称欢乐节。

sentences.english: We’ll do our best to advance the ship- ment to September.
sentences.chinese: 我们尽力把交货期提前到九月份。

sentences.english: Ren Jinxiang is waiting until September to seed rape on her field.
sentences.chinese: 任金祥等待着九月份在田地上播种油菜籽苗。

sentences.english: I don't know, but she did it rightafter she dumped me in September.
sentences.chinese: 不知道，不过她在九月份甩了我之后就立即剪掉了。

sentences.english: The new term will begin in september.
sentences.chinese: 新学期将于九月份开学。

sentences.english: Do you have the September issue of Ivy League AnalyticalEnglish available here?
sentences.chinese: 你这里有卖九月份的《常春藤解析英语杂志》吗？

sentences.english: The product suddenly took off in September.
sentences.chinese: 该产品在九月份突然热销起来。

sentences.english: Since September the cotton price has spiked, which increased our costs.
sentences.chinese: 自从九月份棉价陡增，我们的成本大幅提高。
